pageContext.claim: Peter Navarro releases 36-page report alleging election fraud 'more than sufficient' to swing victory to Trump. A great report by Peter. Statistically impossible to have lost the 2020 Election. Big protest in D.C. on January 6th. Be there, will be wild!
pageContext.analysis: Navarro, the White House director of the Office of Trade and Manufacturing Policy, is no election and political expert and his report was nothing more than a collection of claims made by Trump that has been tossed out in scores of losing lawsuits across the United States. This tweet also helped set the stage for the Jan. 6 riot, when Trump supporters invaded the Capitol.
